# Author wallet private keys — generated by seed-real-papers.mjs, paired
# with addresses in web/data/authors.json. NEVER commit these — anyone
# with the file can sign as any seeded author. Recovery: re-run the seed
# script on a fork; the script preserves existing keys when they're
# present locally, otherwise mints fresh ones.
web/data/authors-keys.json

